Isn't this the way the game has to be?  From your post it seems you like the realm who is the strongest to be made weaker, i.e. less relic gaurds the more relics you have.<P>But if you do that with everything then there is no incentive to do anything.  Adding DF was to provide incentive to take and defend keeps.  Would you rather it be open to the realm with the least amount of keeps instead?<P>There has to be incentive to do things in game.  We take relics because we get more power.  We take keeps to get in to a dungeon to get better equipment.  We do quests for better equipment.  We kill mobs to get higher levels and get interesting loot.<P>If the game wasn't set up like this we would just sit around and chat.  We could do that with AIM and save ourselves the monthly fee.
